cast.name: 泽伊内普·图格斯·巴亚特 Zeynep Tugçe Bayat

introduction: Ömer's only goal, considered dead by his family and loved ones, is to find Zehra. His efforts in this process introduce him to both his new enemies and Neslihan, who will bring him back to the organization. Neslihan's only goal is to keep her promises despite her losses and not leave the people who need her alone. However, even she is not aware of the dangers she will face. The biggest point that unites these two, even indirectly, is the love of the homeland and the desire to protect it. A new team fighting for the same goal will help them on this path. In this tough war, enemies are more dangerous than before.
